{
  "stem": "4113.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The week before, they took their names off, and was the following week that they were called out and sent to the station and sent away.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So this-- this way I lost-- I found out that they were gassed because there were two brothers who survived the war.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they used to work near the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they saw my father and cousin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And one day a fellow at the camp comes-- he's looking for me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he said he had-- there was a little note amongst the boards, you know, that they shipped from Auschwitz to our camp-- there was a note that they saw my father and my-- my cousin go to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So now I was left alone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There I was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then in October, you know, as they were withdrawing, you know, we had to clean up the mass graves that were there at the camp.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was assigned to work in these mass graves that you saw in the movie.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was in there the mass grave.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I remember I worked with a shovel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And there was a redhead man with a baby next to him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I'm not wanting to hurt the body with a shovel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Was bending down and tried to gently lift him off.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And one of the kapos didn't like the way I worked.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Now, all of a sudden I saw all stars in my eyes, and there was all kinds of-- of stuff from the dead body in my mouth and my eyes, and blood was running down my nose-- because I was working too slow.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "That was an incident that happened in that place.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
